        <updateDate>2021-05-06T13:23:36Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Firearms Safety Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows an individual taxpayer a new refundable tax credit for the sum of amounts paid for any gun safe and for a concealed carry firearms course or firearm safety course. The bill prohibits any requirement to provide information on firearms owned by the taxpayer.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
